'''''Caloosahatchee Manuscripts''''' is the title of a [[sculpture]] designed by American artist [[Jim Sanborn]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elonka.com/kryptos/sanborn.html|title=Jim Sanborn: Sculptor, Photographer, Artist|publisher=Elonka|accessdate=2009-10-18}}</ref>It is currently located at the Old Post Office Building in [[Fort Myers, Florida]].

